Ranger Help for: gaia incarnate
=================================

SYNTAX:      incarnate
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   15
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a high-level Ranger to transform into an avatar of
Gaia herself. While in this form, the Ranger's combat abilities are
greatly enhanced for a duration. Strength, speed, and resilience all
increase dramatically. This is the ultimate expression of the bond
between a Ranger and the earth. Only the most experienced Rangers can
channel this much of Gaia's power without being overwhelmed. Requires
a high guild level to learn and use.
